      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be validated under a quality management system with full traceability of code versions and test coverage reports.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation covers version control and unit tests but lacks independent audit records and formal test coverage metrics required at MRL 5."
    },
    {
