      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification must be provided for the selected turbulence closure and hemolysis damage model, including sensitivity analysis demonstrating insensitivity to model-form choices within the operating range.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model and k-omega SST turbulence closure were adopted without formal model-form uncertainty analysis. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
