      "acceptanceCriteria": "Uncertainty in all model input parameters (viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) must be characterized and propagated through the model using a documented UQ method.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input parameter distributions for hemolysis model coefficients were not sourced from primary experimental data. Flagged as incomplete epistemic gap at MRL 5."
